{"tid":1578614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新春袋之馬會","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:35:48.000Z","uid":40652,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0edec6b59ae45185a12be77ec0a90eb5bcee4cbe","tid":1578614,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"睇左隔離個post有人話因為今晚取消左跑馬<br />\n所以政府會少左近7000萬-1億既稅收<br />\n<br />\n但其實有個地方損失仲大<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會</span></span><br />\n大家都知黑警成日爭人錢<br />\n又成日比收數佬追數追到上狗屋<br />\n係因為係香港，除左馬會之外<br />\n所有既外圍都係由鄉/黑控制<br />\n每次馬/波既季節<br />\n每年鄉黑係經香港既外圍收入<br />\n都係十億十億咁計<br />\n<br />\n如果外圍佬冇收入，黑警又有舊數<br />\n唔知班黑社會會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58382aa6f5898846d1904e0e4cafd7892b21ecb5","tid":1578614,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0145488faa7675036fce5ab18fb4333467071d17","tid":1578614,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推啦喂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgdgb4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkgdgb4b.jpg&h=8361ea83&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}